    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《Eletta》是一款鬼马十足的动作冒险游戏——环境不只是背景，而是你的武器库。用滑稽又狡猾的陷阱戏耍敌人，把日常物件变成灾难制造机。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>逃离只是开始</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >被绑架、囚禁的艾莱塔只有一个念头……逃出去。在试图挣脱牢笼的过程中，她逐渐发现自己被掳走背后的真相，并意识到：在一切为时已晚之前，只有她能做点什么。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3024120/extras/8e200e7ae19520491e80859d438260a1.poster.avif?t=1771395904\" width=600 height=232 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3024120/extras/8e200e7ae19520491e80859d438260a1.webm?t=1771395904\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3024120/extras/8e200e7ae19520491e80859d438260a1.mp4?t=1771395904\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>就地反击</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在这场轻松明快却暗流涌动的冒险中，你将扮演艾莱塔，一个机敏的女孩，决心用手边一切可利用之物摆脱绑架者。从随手布下的陷阱到鬼祟的声东击西——环境，是你最强大的武器。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3024120/extras/596616cc701055ece633ca207384a704.poster.avif?t=1771395904\" width=600 height=232 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3024120/extras/596616cc701055ece633ca207384a704.webm?t=1771395904\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3024120/extras/596616cc701055ece633ca207384a704.mp4?t=1771395904\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>扭转局势：</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >万物皆可为兵：把世界本身化作武器，触发环境机关，撂倒敌人</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >揭开谜团：查清自己被绑的真相，阻止悲剧在他人身上重演</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >轻松调皮的恶作剧：为荒诞一笑，又忍不住暗抽一口凉气</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >应对多样的敌人：不同敌人迫使你保持警觉、愈发出其不意</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >强敌压轴：迎战需要创意与巧思才能击败的独特首领</p></li></ul>",
